member.example:
This sample shows how to call GetStatusAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
AzureKeyCredential credential = new AzureKeyCredential("<key>");
FaceAsync client = new FaceClient(endpoint, credential).GetFaceAsyncClient();

Response<AsyncOperationStatus> response = await client.GetStatusAsync("<operationId>");

This sample shows how to call GetStatusAsync with all parameters.

